              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-cyan-900 mb-2">Interior vs. Exterior Decision Guide</h3>
                <p class="text-cyan-800">
                  Choose interior waterproofing if: minor moisture only, exterior access impossible, budget constraints, or home sale planned within 5 years. Choose exterior waterproofing if: active leaking, high water table, structural water damage, long-term home ownership, or Woodbridge flood zone location.
                </p>
              </div>
